<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Homeserver 2027 Frontend</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --ink: #0f172a;
      --paper: #f3efe5;
      --accent: #0f766e;
      --accent-soft: #d8efe8;
      --frame: #d8d1c2;
    }
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      font-family: "Noto Sans", "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      color: var(--ink);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.18), transparent 30%),
        linear-gradient(160deg, #f7f4ec 0%, #ece6da 45%, #f4f0e7 100%);
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      padding: 2rem;
    }
    main {
      width: min(960px, 100%);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
      border: 1px solid var(--frame);
      border-radius: 28px;
      padding: 2.5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12);
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    }
    h1 {
      margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.6rem);
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }
    p {
      margin: 0 0 2rem;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      max-width: 48rem;
    }
    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    a {
      display: block;
      padding: 1.2rem 1.1rem;
      border-radius: 18px;
      border: 1px solid var(--frame);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(216, 239, 232, 0.7), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95));
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      transition: transform 120ms ease, box-shadow 120ms ease;
    }
    a:focus,
    a:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 16px 32px rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.14);
      outline: none;
    }
    .url {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
      font-size: 0.86rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      opacity: 0.75;
      word-break: break-word;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main>
    <h1>Homeserver 2027</h1>
    <p>Shared frontend for the internal services used by Wolf and Franz. This page stays local to the Surface Go and avoids running any extra webserver on the device.</p>
    <section class="grid">
{% for link in surface_go_portal_links %}
      <a href="{{ link.url }}">
        {{ link.label }}
        <span class="url">{{ link.url }}</span>
      </a>
{% endfor %}
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
